checks.prompt:
You are a content strategy director. Synthesize the following research inputs into a Q1 content sprint strategy:

Market research:
{market_data}

Competitor analysis:
{competitor_data}

Audience profiles:
{audience_data}

Produce:
1. Content strategy statement (2 sentences)
2. Priority content types (ranked list of 5)
3. Key messages per persona (3 personas × 1 key message)
4. Estimated content production cost breakdown: { blog_posts: <n_items × $cost_per_item>, case_studies: ..., webinars: ..., total_usd: <number> }

Output ONLY JSON: { "strategy": "...", "content_types": [...], "key_messages": {...}, "cost_breakdown": { "blog_posts": { "count": <n>, "cost_usd": <n> }, "case_studies": { "count": <n>, "cost_usd": <n> }, "webinars": { "count": <n>, "cost_usd": <n> }, "total_usd": <n> } }
